{"tid":1609263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不完美 但可接受]沙田檢討","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T15:58:51.000Z","uid":109953,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4c50bf380dace63bdf96ac5ba7fc9b2a46fd7324","tid":1609263,"uid":109953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:07:52.000Z","msg":"前日有巴打檢討話唔夠哨兵<br />\n自問係和理非都即刻諗方法去做哨兵通水<br />\n不過資訊都人力都太分散<br />\n成班坐曬係中間位無作為<br />\n已經係咁放風話瀝源橋得幾隻畜龍都無人反攻<br />\n建議係：快閃、一係退一係攻，唔好諗住守<br />\n要補給長期戰一定唔夠狗玩，仲有應該要有明確攻略目標，eg狗車、單位、據點，攻完就撤或者去另一個目標<br />\n不完美 但可接受 不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79384dc301af1f282aafaa606fb49c4bbf7335ed","tid":1609263,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:08:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1609038/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1609038/page/1</a><br />\n九龍塘九龍塘九龍塘九龍塘"},{"pid":"4ea6dd3065dae1b1fb5614d4ecf40db2abbffb97","tid":1609263,"uid":109953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:09:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"323c5ea65b2d9b841195829729ef58265c57e7df","tid":1609263,"uid":100133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:12:05.000Z","msg":"問題係勇武唔夠<br />\n個個full gear坐係後面睇電話"},{"pid":"2bdb59778afae9e9d1bcbbe05bea7e3f8631b135","tid":1609263,"uid":307280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:13:32.000Z","msg":"希望下次有個詳細plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d734472e5ef4a0240d0bcbe6174916e9e09028","tid":1609263,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:13:59.000Z","msg":"最值得讚係有工場制造火魔法<br />\n再有人傳送出去"},{"pid":"ed54ccea5ca89ff9428275568172e0daa773c4cf","tid":1609263,"uid":131238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:16:02.000Z","msg":